HEADWORD: Undergrowth
<hw>Un"der*growth`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which
grows under trees; specifically, shrubs or small trees growing among
large trees.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

